com.argox.sdk.barcodeprinter.emulation.pplb

Enum PPLBFont

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<PPLBFont>
      • com.argox.sdk.barcodeprinter.emulation.pplb.PPLBFont
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<PPLBFont>

    public enum PPLBFont
extends java.lang.Enum<PPLBFont>
    This enumeration is used to set the printer's internal fonts and soft fonts.

    The size of the bitmap font.

    Font203 dpi Width * Heigth300 dpi Width * Heigth
    18 * 1212 * 20
    210 * 1616 * 28
    312 * 2020 * 36
    414 * 2424 * 44
    532 * 4848 * 80
    614 * 1914 * 19
    714 * 1914 * 19
